headline: Canadian Natural Q4 Earnings Miss Estimates, Revenues Beat
summary: CNQ expects a total production volume of 1,510-1,555 MBOE/d for 2025. Natural Gas production is expected to be between 2,425 MMcf/d and 2,480 MMcf/d.
